description._content: Description: Fine Aleppo Pine group (Pinus halepensis) with Golden Oak - Quercus alnifolia, underneath. Elidges, Paphos Forest, Elevation 2,950 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Description: Aleppo Pine over 200 years old, showing big bole with Golden Oak in the back ground. Elidges, Paphos Forest, Elevation 2,950 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
